MOST IMMEDIATE/
No.1/34/1/2011-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 13th July, 2011
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 13th July, 2011:-
(i)
Shri Gurudas Kamat relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State
(Independent Charge) of the Ministry of Drinking Water and Sanitation; and
Shri Jairam Ramesh assumed the additional charge of the Ministry of Drinking
Water and Sanitation. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of the
Minister of Rural Development.
(ii)
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 5802
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to the Deputy Chairman and Members of the Planning
Commission.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary

Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
(K.L. Sharma)

(K.L. Sharma)
